Cheparinov, Ivan (2649) - Niemann, Hans Moke (2659)
Tournament of Peace (chess24.com) [6] 2023.11.27
A29 English, four knights, kingside fianchetto

1.c4 Nf6 2.Nc3 e5 3.Nf3 Nc6 4.g3 Bb4 5.Nd5 e4 6.Nh4 O-O 7.a3 Bc5 8.Bg2 d6 9.O-O Re8 10.d3 exd3 11.Qxd3 Ne5 12.Qc2 c6 13.Nc3 Nxc4 14.Na4 Be6 15.Rd1 Bxf2+ 16.Kxf2 Ng4+ 17.Ke1 b5 18.Rd4 Nce3 19.Bxe3 Nxe3 20.Qc3 Bd5 21.Be4 Bxe4 22.Qxe3 Bd5 23.Qd2 bxa4 24.Rxa4 Re5 25.Rd4 g5

The Tournament of Peace is a 10-player round-robin tournament taking place from 22–30 November 2023 in Zagreb, Croatia.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.turnir-mira.com
